    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This engine retains its signature urgency, with the double-VANOS system recently serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and torque delivery across the rev range. The power is channeled through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional traction out of apexes. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, mitigating a known platform fatigue point. Suspension kinematics are sharp, featuring refreshed control arm bushings and tuned dampers that preserve the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and communicative steering rack. While the exterior shows honest signs of road use, the drivetrain and structural components are dialed in for high-performance driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
